* side effects make programming more difficult
	\ links-to internal zuvhnxrfcdqijbje
* makes laziness difficult
	* laziness is automation of evaluation order, which though is error-prone to change in the presence of side-effects
* maked parallel programming difficult
	* data race: multiple threads accessing the same variable, at least 1 of them to write
